  "detailed_description": "<h1>Make your home sparkling!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/e9d15d7afc027156a9bdaf83b993f8ac.avif?t=1772361410\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Home Cleaning is a cozy, family-friendly game where you tidy up a baby’s messes in a playful environment. Use various cleaning utensils to clean rooms, and enjoy the satisfaction of a sparkling home!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361410\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/908bd38951c2f02cf82b748e48f2b96b.poster.avif?t=1772361410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/908bd38951c2f02cf82b748e48f2b96b.webm?t=1772361410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/908bd38951c2f02cf82b748e48f2b96b.mp4?t=1772361410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361410\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Home Cleaning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Home Cleaning is a wholesome, family-friendly game where players tidy up a baby’s messes around the house. With fun, interactive point-and-click gameplay, each level invites players to bring order to a cozy, lively home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361410\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/e81a35c80fd8ced1e748cea9394a3e06.poster.avif?t=1772361410\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/e81a35c80fd8ced1e748cea9394a3e06.webm?t=1772361410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/e81a35c80fd8ced1e748cea9394a3e06.mp4?t=1772361410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351020/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361410\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a variety of cleaning tasks, using different utensils to solve light puzzles and uncover hidden messes. The warm visuals and satisfying gameplay make Home Cleaning a relaxing escape, offering a calming, feel-good experience with each sparkling result.</p>",
